Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.43,0:00:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍華 妳收到過郵局送來的信嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.55,0:00:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是電子郵件哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.68,0:00:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…不多呢 也就是派對的邀請函吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.48,0:00:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 也就只有那個了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.82,0:00:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說電子郵件也很不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.89,0:00:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過還是實體的信好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.84,0:00:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如不幸之信嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.12,0:00:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是決鬥書
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.32,0:00:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那些吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.41,0:00:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小愛 新威尼斯快要進入春天了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.05,0:00:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連太陽公公也一天一天地…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.68,0:00:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變得暖洋洋的了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.29,0:00:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是白天 也會睏意連連…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.53,0:00:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好重啊…亞利亞社長…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.75,0:00:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不覺地就睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.63,0:01:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞利亞社長 謝謝你叫醒我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.48,0:01:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郵遞員老伯？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.29,0:01:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳醒了啊 白天打盹很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.85,0:01:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀…郵遞員老伯看到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.09,0:01:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我從下面看到妳在打盹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.03,0:01:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得叫醒妳就太可憐了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.94,0:01:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.32,0:01:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天呀 我是以顧客的身份來這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.34,0:01:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實呢 老伯我的鳳尾舟破了個洞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.73,0:01:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大約需要一整天來修理
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.60,0:01:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以呢 我想明天把妳們的船包下來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.92,0:01:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用來收發郵件
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.93,0:01:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.53,0:01:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.65,0:01:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 我馬上就去問一下艾莉西亞前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.83,0:01:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.98,0:03:36.98,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(320,270)\blur9\be1\fsp2}那顆 新威尼斯色的心…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.60,0:03:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.87,0:03:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天跟我預約的客人實在太多了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.00,0:03:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.66,0:03:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.32,0:03:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 小姑娘妳來做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.65,0:03:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀 燈里還是見習領航員
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.47,0:04:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有指導人員在場 是沒辦法讓客人乘坐的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.39,0:04:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.84,0:04:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.38,0:04:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天的工作能不能找別人代替呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.50,0:04:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.59,0:04:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郵局的人都說這是個好機會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.46,0:04:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾脆就休息一天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.50,0:04:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這個與其說是工作 不如說是老伯我的興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.86,0:04:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢 我捨不得休息啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.91,0:04:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不行的話 就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.34,0:04:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思啊 委託這麼奇怪的工作給妳們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.78,0:04:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燈里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.00,0:04:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.96,0:04:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾除了自主練習之外
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.07,0:04:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再請一些不同的人來指導怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.37,0:04:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如說 郵遞員先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.94,0:04:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.76,0:04:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要不是客人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.08,0:04:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是作為指導人員來指導我練習的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.22,0:04:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 這樣小姑娘既能練習
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.17,0:05:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而老伯我也能收發郵件
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.83,0:05:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是一舉兩得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.70,0:05:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 社長先生也要一起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.41,0:05:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳 艾莉西亞前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.83,0:05:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.90,0:05:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那明天就拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.03,0:05:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 彼此彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.91,0:05:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,康納瑞橋郵政局
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.88,0:05:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這裡了 亞利亞社長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.06,0:05:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.56,0:05:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.18,0:05:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是今天來給郵遞員老伯幫忙的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.22,0:05:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郵遞員老伯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.55,0:05:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.26,0:05:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對了 好像大家都是郵遞員呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.96,0:05:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.92,0:05:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 我還不知道老伯的名字…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.90,0:06:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 妳就是長老經常提起的那個領航員小姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.79,0:06:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長老？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.21,0:06:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 請裡面走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.80,0:06:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好宏偉的建築啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.73,0:06:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有墨水的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.21,0:06:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這裡是郵局啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.65,0:06:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 小姑娘 妳來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.21,0:06:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老伯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.94,0:06:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.15,0:06:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.88,0:06:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼早就讓妳來 真是不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.45,0:06:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天一天請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.21,0:06:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡哪裡 彼此彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.25,0:06:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社長先生 今天跟老伯戴一樣的帽子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.84,0:07:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.62,0:07:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 開始了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.49,0:07:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是早操哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.93,0:07:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為老伯的工作是體力活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.77,0:07:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能有點不好意思啦 不過這也是個儀式
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.84,0:07:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就陪我們做一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.18,0:07:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.90,0:07:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 那麼我們出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.25,0:07:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.84,0:07:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郵遞員老伯被稱為長老呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.75,0:08:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也有年輕人管我叫老伯啦 老爹什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.26,0:08:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過啊 老伯我就是個郵遞員老伯而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.24,0:08:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 要開始工作了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.90,0:08:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 靠近點 靠近點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.33,0:08:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.17,0:08:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼看都是如此精準迅速啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.95,0:08:49.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘 要不也來試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.26,0:08:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.04,0:08:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就試試那個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.78,0:08:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.48,0:09:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對對對…對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.45,0:09:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.19,0:09:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 放回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.90,0:09:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.74,0:09:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安全放回原處了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.91,0:09:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 第一次能這樣很不錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.18,0:09:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.38,0:10:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那接下來的慢慢來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.44,0:10:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.40,0:10:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.95,0:10:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賣力工作過後肚子一定餓了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.51,0:10:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 午飯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.03,0:10:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.74,0:10:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.40,0:10:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個煎蛋捲好好吃～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.34,0:10:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.29,0:10:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.56,0:10:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再繼續努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.91,0:10:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下午還要配送信件哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.25,0:10:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.36,0:11:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 亞利亞社長？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.76,0:11:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 社長
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.57,0:11:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要寄信嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.28,0:11:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.37,0:11:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這封信 我希望能立刻送到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.36,0:11:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 今天已經過了收信的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.75,0:11:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最快也要等到明天了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.53,0:11:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不送出去的話就來不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.33,0:11:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收信人住很遠嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.71,0:11:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那直接放進郵箱不是更快嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.77,0:11:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 因為典禮已經開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.27,0:11:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,典禮？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.72,0:11:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結婚典禮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.43,0:11:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結婚典禮？誰的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.66,0:11:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.84,0:12:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 這是給老師的祝賀信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.34,0:12:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是新娘嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.74,0:12:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面寫了「恭賀新婚」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.75,0:12:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也寫了「對不起」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.33,0:12:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師辭職之前 有一個合唱比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.71,0:12:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我沒有參加
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.64,0:12:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽期間 我一直躲在音樂室
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.88,0:12:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓老師傷透腦筋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.43,0:12:31.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在歡送會那天 我甚至還說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.02,0:12:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「老師不在以後可就輕鬆了」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.92,0:12:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當時第一次看到老師流淚了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.31,0:12:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那封信給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.22,0:12:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我幫你送到教堂去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.39,0:13:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你也要一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.68,0:13:01.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.12,0:13:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘 可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.95,0:13:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以 當然沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.55,0:13:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是亞利亞公司的領航員 水無燈里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.85,0:13:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.71,0:13:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.87,0:13:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小空 真好聽的名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.75,0:13:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘 趕快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.40,0:13:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我用逆划過去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.05,0:13:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逆划？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.97,0:13:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.48,0:13:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.70,0:13:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 就這樣一直前進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.01,0:13:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.42,0:14:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎趕上了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.37,0:14:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.32,0:14:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我給你去送信啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.24,0:14:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜妳 綾乃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.95,0:14:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.15,0:14:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝妳幸福 綾乃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.72,0:14:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.31,0:14:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.41,0:14:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師 恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.85,0:14:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.47,0:14:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師 恭喜妳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.14,0:14:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾乃老師 恭喜妳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.86,0:14:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝大家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.67,0:14:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有您的信
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.51,0:14:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.30,0:14:54.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寄信人是小空
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.13,0:15:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師 總是給妳惹麻煩 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.47,0:15:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡送會的時候說了這麼過分的話 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.89,0:15:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙妳說「很輕鬆」 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.94,0:15:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實…我最喜歡老師妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.64,0:15:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想到妳就要離開 就覺得很寂寞…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.46,0:15:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法對妳說「恭喜」 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.53,0:15:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師 恭喜妳結婚了 要幸福哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.33,0:15:39.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.55,0:15:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小空
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.54,0:15:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郵遞員先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.13,0:15:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.79,0:16:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送信完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.93,0:16:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師很高興哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.29,0:16:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.81,0:16:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 太好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.37,0:16:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.66,0:16:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.19,0:16:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小空真正的溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.83,0:16:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彷彿從信的字裡行間傳到我的心中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.12,0:16:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對小空而言 那就是他的最高祝福吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.84,0:17:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 對那孩子來說 我是個好老師嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.23,0:17:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.61,0:17:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小空
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.46,0:17:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.17,0:17:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小空 謝謝你的信
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.56,0:17:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.86,0:17:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會給你回信的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.12,0:17:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜妳 老師 要保重哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.58,0:17:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.31,0:17:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.92,0:18:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 再見 小空
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.87,0:18:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郵遞員伯伯 謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.18,0:18:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.04,0:18:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 剩下的信件也要趕緊送出去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.75,0:18:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.40,0:18:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後一封信送完了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.93,0:18:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.06,0:18:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳 小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.65,0:19:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新娘子好像很高興呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.84,0:19:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小空也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.01,0:19:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郵遞員老伯不捨得休息的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.01,0:19:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像也有點明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.46,0:19:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.21,0:19:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真是一份很有意義的工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.71,0:19:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.28,0:19:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天轉了一整天 我才發現到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.86,0:19:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新威尼斯有很多郵筒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.67,0:19:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 因為這裡的人還是習慣於寫信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.95,0:19:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特意做這種麻煩的事 一點都不方便
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.10,0:19:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢 這是為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.89,0:19:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概 如果太急了 心情就沒法平靜下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.33,0:19:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信這種東西 收到的時候會很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.05,0:19:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打開的時候就像打開寶箱一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.10,0:20:02.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心情會變得像孩子一樣興奮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.67,0:20:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且裡面是以書信的形式表現出的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.52,0:20:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寄信人的心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.45,0:20:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據內容的不同
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.30,0:20:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時就會變成自己的寶物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.76,0:20:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變成一輩子都能用手觸碰到的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.24,0:20:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫做「心」的寶物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.00,0:20:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠用手觸碰的「心」…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.65,0:20:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 信件能跨越時空的界限
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.97,0:20:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把寫信的人帶到自己面前來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.16,0:20:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新威尼斯城也和信件有相似之處呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.60,0:20:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為創造這座城市的人們的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.76,0:20:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論何時都能用雙手觸碰到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.51,0:21:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.04,0:21:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來我啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.07,0:21:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很喜歡這個特意做麻煩事的城市呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.81,0:21:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 小姑娘妳已經染上新威尼斯的顏色了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.62,0:21:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.06,0:21:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.76,0:21:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 燈里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.05,0:21:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 艾莉西亞前輩 這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.56,0:21:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這是今早送來的寫給燈里的信
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.60,0:21:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是郵遞員老伯寄來的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.72,0:21:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,致小姑娘：
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.19,0:21:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.03,0:22:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郵遞員老伯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.87,0:22:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和郵遞員老伯說的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.33,0:22:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信件會把寫信的人帶到眼前呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.99,0:22:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小愛 那封信雖然很短
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.74,0:22:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但褪色的墨水字跡卻令人感受到濃濃的暖意
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.71,0:22:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面還有郵遞員先生那淡淡的煙味呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.94,0:22:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燈里姐姐 妳又多了一樣寶物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.62,0:22:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫信啊…說起來我還真的沒寫過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.95,0:22:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次試著寫寫看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.29,0:22:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣我也能接近新威尼斯的色彩了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.92,0:24:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那份 雨天的精彩…\N那個 春日的發現…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OPJP】
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.95,0:02:15.85,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}窓からそっと 朝陽がのびて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.24,0:02:28.83,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}まどろむまつ毛に こぼれてくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.17,0:02:43.87,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}そよふく風 部屋へと招いて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.91,0:02:56.68,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}木漏れ日に 君の寝顔 優しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.06,0:02:56.68,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\an7}Euforia
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.78,0:03:03.00,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}いつものありふれた朝だけど
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.68,0:03:10.61,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}鮮やかに色づいてるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.88,0:03:18.09,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}それは君と巡り合えた奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.67,0:03:21.63,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}ひとりじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.19,0:03:28.40,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}君と一緒にいるから
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OPCH】
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.95,0:02:15.85,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}晨曦悄然漫入窗際
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.24,0:02:28.83,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}灑落在 舒睡的睫毛間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.17,0:02:43.87,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}讓輕拂的風吹入小屋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.91,0:02:56.68,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}枝葉間滑落的陽光 映襯你的睡顏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.06,0:02:56.68,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\an3}Euforia
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.78,0:03:03.00,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}雖是個平凡無奇的早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.68,0:03:10.61,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}也染上了豔麗的色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.88,0:03:18.09,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}那正是與你邂逅的奇蹟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.67,0:03:21.63,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}我並非孤單一人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.19,0:03:28.40,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}因為 有你相伴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【EDJP】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.17,0:22:57.14,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}雨が上がる 遠く空眺め 雲の切れ間探す
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.99,0:23:08.99,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}いつもよりも 少し遠回り 海へ続く道を
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.65,0:23:16.72,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}切りすぎた前髪 気にしないで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.87,0:23:21.33,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}そのまま 駆け出そう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.16,0:23:28.21,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}頬をかすめていく 風の色が
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.34,0:23:33.81,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}いつか夏のはじまりを告げる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.95,0:23:40.02,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}大きく手を振って 深呼吸しよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.22,0:23:45.63,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}この時間を抱きしめていたいから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.83,0:23:50.77,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}明日もまた会えるかな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【EDCH】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.17,0:22:57.14,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}雨過天晴 眺望遙遠的天空 探尋雲彩的縫隙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.99,0:23:08.99,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}繞過早已習慣的歸途 向著通往大海的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.65,0:23:16.72,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}忘掉剪得過短的留海
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.87,0:23:21.33,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}毫無顧忌地大膽前進
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.16,0:23:28.21,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}吹拂著面頰的海風
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.34,0:23:33.81,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}不知何時染上了初夏的色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.95,0:23:40.02,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}用力揮揮手 來個深呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.22,0:23:45.63,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}滿心希望永遠擁抱這一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.83,0:23:50.77,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}明天 我們還會再見嗎


